|**Build**|Innovation Project (with Implementation Partner)|CHF 100K-500K (Innosuisse covers research partner; FactHarbor co-funds 40-60%, mostly as developer time)|Duration: up to 36 months|Joint R&D on resource-efficient fact verification — distillation, multilingual robustness, evaluation frameworks
