(((
The roadmap below combines core platform work with the most important missing user-facing, integration, and cooperation-oriented capabilities. Post-V1.0 feature milestones use finer-grained labels such as V1.1+ and V1.5+. The federation diagram remains as the long-term architecture target.
)))

