|**Professional workflows**|API clients / SDKs; team workspaces; expert review workflow|V1.0 / V1.5+
|**Cooperation features**|Collaborative annotation; comparative fact-check view; shared benchmarks and evaluation datasets|V1.5+ / V2.0+
|**Federated cooperation**|Claim synchronization; cross-node contradiction detection; distributed verdict agreement|V2.0+

=== Target: Federated Network (V2.0+) ===

The long-term vision is a **federated architecture** — independent FactHarbor instances operated by different organizations can synchronize verified claims while maintaining local control and autonomy.

